{
  "id": "690f77827cd288ac167efd39",
  "title": "2025/11/09",
  "created": 1762621315,
  "updated": 1776342698,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "690f77827cd288ac167efd39",
      "text": "2025/11/09",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762621315,
      "updated": 1762621315
    },
    {
      "id": "690f77826eb4060000004996d9",
      "text": "第46週: [[日]]月火水木金土",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762621315,
      "updated": 1762621315
    },
    {
      "id": "690f77826eb4060000001751f6",
      "text": "2025年 85.75％経過",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762621315,
      "updated": 1762621315
    },
    {
      "id": "690f77826eb406000000945ca6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762621315,
      "updated": 1762621315
    },
    {
      "id": "690f77826eb406000000d6738c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762621315,
      "updated": 1762621315
    },
    {
      "id": "690f77826eb406000000e5614c",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762621315,
      "updated": 1762621340
    },
    {
      "id": "690f779b00000000001b12fb",
      "text": " 今日メガネを買いに行く予定",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762621340,
      "updated": 1762621347
    },
    {
      "id": "690f77a300000000001b12fc",
      "text": "  眼鏡を買いに行くメガネがない、となる前に",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762621348,
      "updated": 1762621359
    },
    {
      "id": "690f77af00000000001b12fd",
      "text": "  まぁ[JINS]とかで安いのを買うつもりだが",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762621360,
      "updated": 1762621388
    },
    {
      "id": "690f77fc00000000001b12fe",
      "text": "  今のは[JINS]の[Airframe]だったはず",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762621437,
      "updated": 1762621485
    },
    {
      "id": "690f784300000000001b12ff",
      "text": "   子供に踏まれても折れなそうという理由でヒンジレスにした",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762621508,
      "updated": 1762621532
    },
    {
      "id": "690f785c00000000001b1300",
      "text": "   今はもうその懸念はなさそうなのでなんでも良いなぁ",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762621533,
      "updated": 1762621545
    },
    {
      "id": "690f7a610000000000b4b151",
      "text": "   2021年に買ってる。案外持たないな",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762622050,
      "updated": 1762622059
    },
    {
      "id": "690f7c250000000000b4b152",
      "text": "  特徴的なメガネにすると顔を覚えてもらいやすくなるが、メガネを変えると誰だかわからなくなる諸刃の剣",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762622503,
      "updated": 1762622554
    },
    {
      "id": "691008a200000000003dfdde",
      "text": "  5歳の娘に見てもらいながら選んだら今のと同じ感じのフレームに落ち着いた",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762658467,
      "updated": 1762658486
    },
    {
      "id": "6910233d0000000000c94c21",
      "text": "   6000円くらい(店舗の中では一番安かったように思う)",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762665293,
      "updated": 1762665321
    },
    {
      "id": "691008b500000000003dfddf",
      "text": "   その他の感想",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762658486,
      "updated": 1762665310
    },
    {
      "id": "691008ba00000000003dfde0",
      "text": "    スーパーマンみたい",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762658492,
      "updated": 1762658495
    },
    {
      "id": "691015b30000000000d2b99c",
      "text": "     横長のスクエア",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762661812,
      "updated": 1762661847
    },
    {
      "id": "691008be00000000003dfde1",
      "text": "    泥棒みたい",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762658495,
      "updated": 1762658498
    },
    {
      "id": "691015b70000000000d2b99d",
      "text": "     フレームが濃い色で太め",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762661816,
      "updated": 1762661824
    },
    {
      "id": "691008f500000000003dfde2",
      "text": "    ロボットみたい",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762658552,
      "updated": 1762658553
    },
    {
      "id": "691015c20000000000d2b99e",
      "text": "     スクエア",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762661827,
      "updated": 1762661829
    },
    {
      "id": "691010050000000000a03b2b",
      "text": "   ほのぼの[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762660358,
      "updated": 1762660363
    },
    {
      "id": "690f77826eb406000000cadc1c",
      "text": " カラオケに挑戦した5歳の娘",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762621315,
      "updated": 1762670854
    },
    {
      "id": "6910392e0000000000a6918a",
      "text": "  上手く歌えず泣き出してしまった",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762670895,
      "updated": 1762670902
    },
    {
      "id": "69103edd0000000000a6918b",
      "text": "  苦手意識を植え付けてないか心配",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762672350,
      "updated": 1762672360
    },
    {
      "id": "69103fe90000000000a6918d",
      "text": "   まぁだいたいこういうのは杞憂",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762672618,
      "updated": 1762672626
    },
    {
      "id": "69103ff90000000000a6918e",
      "text": "   早めに転ぶ体験できてよかったね、くらいに思っておこう",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762672634,
      "updated": 1762672648
    },
    {
      "id": "691038f70000000000a69189",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762670840,
      "updated": 1762670840
    },
    {
      "id": "690fb0980000000000d44633",
      "text": "[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1762635927,
      "updated": 1762635928
    },
    {
      "id": "690fb0980000000000d44634",
      "text": " [Detroit: Become Human]の実況見てたらアンドロイドと一緒に暮らしたいなぁと思えてきた",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1762635928,
      "updated": 1762635961
    },
    {
      "id": "690fb0ac0000000000d44635",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1762635948,
      "updated": 1762635949
    },
    {
      "id": "690fc200000000000010c322",
      "text": "[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1762640385,
      "updated": 1762640386
    },
    {
      "id": "690fc202000000000010c323",
      "text": "\t[ハエトリグモ]を指に乗せたいが難しい",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1762640386,
      "updated": 1762640410
    },
    {
      "id": "690fc20e000000000010c324",
      "text": "\t\t障害物とみなされているようだ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1762640399,
      "updated": 1762640402
    },
    {
      "id": "69101f780000000000589e81",
      "text": "\t\t元気だ、LDKを一周してる感じで、今ちょうどモニタの先の壁を這ってる",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1762664314,
      "updated": 1762664333
    },
    {
      "id": "69101f990000000000589e83",
      "text": "\t\tなんとなくコバエを殺してくれてる気がするので見逃してあげよう",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1762664346,
      "updated": 1762664353
    },
    {
      "id": "690fc211000000000010c325",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1762640402,
      "updated": 1762640406
    },
    {
      "id": "690fc2dd0000000000cf0966",
      "text": "[Hyou.icon]",
      "userId": "657c19a3646988002500645a",
      "created": 1762640606,
      "updated": 1762640607
    },
    {
      "id": "690fc2dd0000000000cf0967",
      "text": "　おもはゆい",
      "userId": "657c19a3646988002500645a",
      "created": 1762640606,
      "updated": 1762640610
    },
    {
      "id": "69105ec60000000000cf0969",
      "text": "　身体が悲鳴を上げてる",
      "userId": "657c19a3646988002500645a",
      "created": 1762680524,
      "updated": 1762680530
    },
    {
      "id": "69105ed20000000000cf096a",
      "text": "　　身体 < ｷｭｰ",
      "userId": "657c19a3646988002500645a",
      "created": 1762680531,
      "updated": 1762680543
    },
    {
      "id": "691075fe00000000001d6a85",
      "text": "　　🐬かな？[Hiro Aki.icon]",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1762686463,
      "updated": 1762686472
    },
    {
      "id": "690fc2dd0000000000cf0968",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "657c19a3646988002500645a",
      "created": 1762640606,
      "updated": 1762640606
    },
    {
      "id": "690feccb0000000000c81cdf",
      "text": "[nomadoor.icon]",
      "userId": "5f0ae250e8cd56001ee2dacc",
      "created": 1762651419,
      "updated": 1762651421
    },
    {
      "id": "690feccc0000000000c81ce0",
      "text": " Realforceが壊れたけど、ノリではんだ付けしてたら直った",
      "userId": "5f0ae250e8cd56001ee2dacc",
      "created": 1762651421,
      "updated": 1762651433
    },
    {
      "id": "690fecd90000000000c81ce2",
      "text": " 　なんで直ったのかわからないけど動いているのでヨシ[ヨシ!.icon]",
      "userId": "5f0ae250e8cd56001ee2dacc",
      "created": 1762651433,
      "updated": 1762651465
    },
    {
      "id": "69102fb80000000000a03b33",
      "text": " 　一瞬「糊ではんだ付け」と解釈した[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762668472,
      "updated": 1762668495
    },
    {
      "id": "69102fcf0000000000a03b34",
      "text": " 　 なんで動いてるのか謎だなと思ったw",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762668495,
      "updated": 1762668506
    },
    {
      "id": "690fefe40000000000358f04",
      "text": "　やっぱりドキュメント形式のほうが読まれやすいかなぁと思って、work4aiに書いたものを階層構造に整えてみるも、あちらこちらでコウモリが問題を起こしてきてツライ",
      "userId": "5f0ae250e8cd56001ee2dacc",
      "created": 1762652133,
      "updated": 1762679849
    },
    {
      "id": "69105bdb0000000000182b70",
      "text": "　　やはりScrapboxは神……",
      "userId": "5f0ae250e8cd56001ee2dacc",
      "created": 1762679852,
      "updated": 1762680051
    },
    {
      "id": "69105ca20000000000182b71",
      "text": "　　ただ、ある程度の習熟度までは、マニュアルは一方通行であったほうが学ぶ側からしたら楽なのでバランスを取って行きたいところ",
      "userId": "5f0ae250e8cd56001ee2dacc",
      "created": 1762680051,
      "updated": 1762680618
    },
    {
      "id": "69105b9e0000000000182b6f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f0ae250e8cd56001ee2dacc",
      "created": 1762679791,
      "updated": 1762679791
    },
    {
      "id": "690fefe50000000000358f05",
      "text": "[zatto.icon]",
      "userId": "67026b2a4d8cae001d9e390a",
      "created": 1762652134,
      "updated": 1762652137
    },
    {
      "id": "690fefec0000000000358f06",
      "text": "　なんか井戸端がシャニマスだ！",
      "userId": "67026b2a4d8cae001d9e390a",
      "created": 1762652141,
      "updated": 1762652155
    },
    {
      "id": "69100408000000000037783c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1762657294,
      "updated": 1762657294
    },
    {
      "id": "69100409000000000037783d",
      "text": "[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1762657294,
      "updated": 1762657295
    },
    {
      "id": "6910040b000000000037783e",
      "text": "\tタスク渋滞にはGTD",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1762657296,
      "updated": 1762657423
    },
    {
      "id": "69104baa0000000000ea9651",
      "text": "\tちょっとしたダイブルチェックというか検証をしていて、手で（人の目で）数えたら97なんだけど、プログラムで数えたら106あって、何が重なっていないのかわからず困り。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1762675627,
      "updated": 1762675702
    },
    {
      "id": "6910593b00000000007685ad",
      "text": "\t\tはあ、一致した。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1762679100,
      "updated": 1762679235
    },
    {
      "id": "691059c300000000007685af",
      "text": "\t\t目に入っていなかった何箇所かが発覚して105だった。プログラムのミスが発覚して修正したら105だった。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1762679235,
      "updated": 1762679235
    },
    {
      "id": "6910595300000000007685ae",
      "text": "\t\t人も計算機も、数さえ数えられない😢",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1762679123,
      "updated": 1762679135
    },
    {
      "id": "69108e9d00000000001a519b",
      "text": "\t感覚や経験は大事とはいえ、主要なアウトプット手段は言語なのだから、たいした知のストックのない存在に「学び合ってもらう」なんてことは成立しない。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1762692766,
      "updated": 1762692809
    },
    {
      "id": "69108f1400000000001a519d",
      "text": "\t\t幸い人間という動物はすぐに狩りをしたり天敵から身を守らずとも20歳くらいまで目先の有用性を留保して知のストックを貯められる猶予期間（モラトリアム）が許される。文化的。他の動物との差異の1つ。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1762692885,
      "updated": 1762693153
    },
    {
      "id": "69108ed100000000001a519c",
      "text": "\t\tもし主体性らしきものがあるように見えるとしたら、それは家庭や地域のハビトゥスの再生産に過ぎないわけで。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1762692818,
      "updated": 1762692863
    },
    {
      "id": "69108f7400000000001a519e",
      "text": "\t\t知のストックがない状態で他者から評価されるような振る舞いだけ反射として身につけ続けることの行き着く先は、詐欺さえも上手い人。老人に“上手に”不要なものを売りつけられる、という「コミュ力」（目先で有用とされる何か）が高い人。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1762692981,
      "updated": 1762693102
    },
    {
      "id": "690feccc0000000000c81ce1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f0ae250e8cd56001ee2dacc",
      "created": 1762651421,
      "updated": 1762651421
    },
    {
      "id": "691006270000000000a03b22",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762657832,
      "updated": 1762657834
    },
    {
      "id": "6910062a0000000000a03b23",
      "text": " [ルノワール]面白いな",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762657834,
      "updated": 1762662509
    },
    {
      "id": "691006300000000000a03b24",
      "text": "  https://x.com/sugokuaki/status/1987126849311547442?s=46&t=gkSZtjGEtUZPO0JCzBxCBw",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762657840,
      "updated": 1762657843
    },
    {
      "id": "691006350000000000a03b25",
      "text": "  この時代に本名顔出しでおっぱい大好きと公表する精神",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762657845,
      "updated": 1762657866
    },
    {
      "id": "691006510000000000a03b27",
      "text": "  「人妻のおっぱいが見たくて泣いちゃう男性怖い」ウケる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762657874,
      "updated": 1762657903
    },
    {
      "id": "691006910000000000a03b28",
      "text": " 仕事(副業)しなきゃ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762657940,
      "updated": 1762658347
    },
    {
      "id": "6910183f0000000000a0e649",
      "text": " 「にちか」だけ印象に残っている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762662463,
      "updated": 1762662472
    },
    {
      "id": "691018490000000000a0e64a",
      "text": " \t独特な名前だからか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762662473,
      "updated": 1762662478
    },
    {
      "id": "69101d970000000000a0e64c",
      "text": " (GPT5)GitHubの仕様で「リポジトリ活動が60日間ないと定期実行ワークフローは自動で無効化」されます。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762663832,
      "updated": 1762663833
    },
    {
      "id": "69101d9a0000000000a0e64d",
      "text": " \tそうなんだ？初耳",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762663834,
      "updated": 1762663844
    },
    {
      "id": "69101f2d0000000000589e7f",
      "text": " \t\t+1[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1762664239,
      "updated": 1762664240
    },
    {
      "id": "69101f310000000000589e80",
      "text": " \t\t\t調べてみるとドキュメントはないが、対象者にはメールで警告されるらしい？",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1762664242,
      "updated": 1762664260
    },
    {
      "id": "69101da40000000000a0e64e",
      "text": " \tGitHub ActionsでCosenseの同期とか翻訳とかする系が時々止まるのってそのせい？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762663844,
      "updated": 1762663874
    },
    {
      "id": "6911355a0000000000a74ed0",
      "text": " \t 自分もプライベート日記をパブリックにコピーするのをGithubActionでやってるけど、時々止まってる。気付いたときに再開するようにしてる[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1762735450,
      "updated": 1762735518
    },
    {
      "id": "691020ac0000000000c94c1d",
      "text": " \tそれで止められてるワークフローがある[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762664621,
      "updated": 1762664633
    },
    {
      "id": "691021e20000000000c94c1e",
      "text": " \t メールも来てる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762664931,
      "updated": 1762664939
    },
    {
      "id": "691021e50000000000c94c1f",
      "text": " \t  > Scheduled workflows are disabled automatically after 60 days of repository inactivity. ",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762664934,
      "updated": 1762664945
    },
    {
      "id": "6911923d00000000007a9a46",
      "text": " \t  [scrapbox-external-backup]がこれでメールきた[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1762759230,
      "updated": 1762759242
    },
    {
      "id": "6910220a0000000000c94c20",
      "text": " \t 自身でcommitするようにすれば動き続けそうだけど、その目的のために仕込むのは行儀が悪いかなと思ってる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1762664971,
      "updated": 1762665003
    },
    {
      "id": "69102853000000000076eeee",
      "text": " \t \t+1[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762666579,
      "updated": 1762666581
    },
    {
      "id": "6910285d000000000076eeef",
      "text": " \t \t\t必要ないのに無償のコンピューテーションリソースを食い続けるのは良くないよねという修正だと思うので、自己コミットで回避するのは非倫理的だと思う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762666590,
      "updated": 1762666636
    },
    {
      "id": "69101f250000000000589e7e",
      "text": " 食人族がいる森に不時着して生き延びるゲーム",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762664232,
      "updated": 1762668350
    },
    {
      "id": "69102f3d0000000000a03b2d",
      "text": "  https://x.com/gerogeror/status/1987345531597955421?s=46&t=gkSZtjGEtUZPO0JCzBxCBw",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762668350,
      "updated": 1762668352
    },
    {
      "id": "69102f430000000000a03b2e",
      "text": "  食人族を食料にすることができる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762668355,
      "updated": 1762668365
    },
    {
      "id": "69102f4d0000000000a03b2f",
      "text": "   は？どっちが食人族だよw",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762668365,
      "updated": 1762668387
    },
    {
      "id": "69102f640000000000a03b32",
      "text": "   [深淵をのぞく時深淵もまたこちらをのぞいているのだ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762668388,
      "updated": 1762668401
    },
    {
      "id": "69104b4200000000008d30ba",
      "text": "   [ミノタウロスの皿]み[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1762675522,
      "updated": 1762675524
    },
    {
      "id": "69102f4e0000000000a03b30",
      "text": " 仕事してません、ぴえん",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762668367,
      "updated": 1762668543
    },
    {
      "id": "691030400000000000a03b35",
      "text": "  ポモドーロ🍅",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762668610,
      "updated": 1762673244
    },
    {
      "id": "691042a90000000000a03b36",
      "text": "  コンフリクトを解消してマージするところをミスった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762673322,
      "updated": 1762673336
    },
    {
      "id": "691042b90000000000a03b37",
      "text": " 仕事終わってない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762673337,
      "updated": 1762684218
    },
    {
      "id": "69106d3a000000000051e77c",
      "text": "  火遊びしようかと思ったら買い物を頼まれてしまった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762684219,
      "updated": 1762684231
    },
    {
      "id": "69106d48000000000051e77d",
      "text": "  まあ[徳を積んでおこう]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1762684232,
      "updated": 1762697212
    },
    {
      "id": "69102f4e0000000000a03b31",
      "text": " 今日の火遊び",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762668367,
      "updated": 1762695939
    },
    {
      "id": "69109b0300000000008bd5ad",
      "text": "  着火剤なしで火起こしできるのでは仮説",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762695939,
      "updated": 1762695967
    },
    {
      "id": "69109b1f00000000008bd5ae",
      "text": "   無事成功",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762695967,
      "updated": 1762695986
    },
    {
      "id": "69109b3200000000008bd5af",
      "text": "   割り箸にライターで火がつくのだからそれを育てたらいけるよね、という実験",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762695986,
      "updated": 1762696006
    },
    {
      "id": "69116cc90000000000428743",
      "text": "    [火を育てる]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762749642,
      "updated": 1762749649
    },
    {
      "id": "69109b4600000000008bd5b0",
      "text": "   着火剤がないからか勉強したからか炎の状態がよくわかった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762696006,
      "updated": 1762696039
    },
    {
      "id": "69109b6700000000008bd5b1",
      "text": "   木が分解してガスが出てるけど炎が出てない状態で息を吹き込むと酸素が供給されて炎がついたりする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762696040,
      "updated": 1762696086
    },
    {
      "id": "69109b9700000000008bd5b2",
      "text": "    なるほどなー",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762696088,
      "updated": 1762696090
    },
    {
      "id": "69109ba700000000008bd5b3",
      "text": "   発電は5ゲージ目まで来た",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762696104,
      "updated": 1762696118
    },
    {
      "id": "69109bf900000000008bd5b4",
      "text": "  木質ペレットを買ったんだけどどのタイミングで入れたらいいのかよくわからん",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762696185,
      "updated": 1762696205
    },
    {
      "id": "69109c0d00000000008bd5b5",
      "text": "\t帰ってきたら臭いと言われた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762696205,
      "updated": 1762706592
    },
    {
      "id": "6910c4a00000000000a0e64f",
      "text": "\t\tうーむ、ウェットティッシュで頭を拭くか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762706592,
      "updated": 1762706624
    },
    {
      "id": "6910c52a0000000000a0e652",
      "text": "\t\t[\" 炎が出てない状態で息を吹き込むと酸素が供給されて炎がついたりする]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762706730,
      "updated": 1762706735
    },
    {
      "id": "6910c52f0000000000a0e653",
      "text": "\t\t\tこれが悪い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762706736,
      "updated": 1762706740
    },
    {
      "id": "6910c53e0000000000a0e654",
      "text": "\t\t\tいらんやろとおもってたけど火吹き棒ってこういう時にいるんだな",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762706750,
      "updated": 1762706772
    },
    {
      "id": "6910c5740000000000a0e655",
      "text": "\t\t今回は青い炎とか色々観察できた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762706805,
      "updated": 1762706827
    },
    {
      "id": "6910c58b0000000000a0e656",
      "text": "\t\t\t炭が主体になった後、酸素が足りなくてCOができて、それが燃えると青い炎",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762706827,
      "updated": 1762706861
    },
    {
      "id": "6910c5b60000000000a0e657",
      "text": "\t\t\tそこに杉を入れると分解してガスが出るが、着火に至らない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762706870,
      "updated": 1762706897
    },
    {
      "id": "6910c5d10000000000a0e658",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t息を吹き込むと炎が出たりする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762706897,
      "updated": 1762706918
    },
    {
      "id": "6910c4c40000000000a0e650",
      "text": "\t仕事終わった & 年末調整も終わった 1:44",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762706629,
      "updated": 1762706658
    },
    {
      "id": "6910c4e30000000000a0e651",
      "text": "\t\t休日も終わってた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762706659,
      "updated": 1762706664
    },
    {
      "id": "69109c0d00000000008bd5b6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1762696205,
      "updated": 1762696205
    },
    {
      "id": "69103a1e0000000000991e4e",
      "text": "[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1762671135,
      "updated": 1762671135
    },
    {
      "id": "69103a1e0000000000991e4f",
      "text": "\t[BOSE QuietComfort 35のイヤーパッド交換]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1762671135,
      "updated": 1762671414
    },
    {
      "id": "69103c5e0000000000991e77",
      "text": "\t\t人間関係はトライアンドエラーしづらい営みだが、こういう「すぐ壊れる部品を扱う」のも結構そうだよなぁ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1762671711,
      "updated": 1762671730
    },
    {
      "id": "69103c710000000000991e78",
      "text": "\t\tこの辺AIで進展しないだろうか",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1762671730,
      "updated": 1762671850
    },
    {
      "id": "69103cf10000000000991e79",
      "text": "\t\t\tまあ普通は？友人やパートナーがいるはずでそれに頼ればいいだけなので中々ニーズないか",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1762671859,
      "updated": 1762671873
    },
    {
      "id": "69103d0d0000000000991e7a",
      "text": "\t\t\tひとりではやり方の不備に気づきにくい",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1762671887,
      "updated": 1762671892
    },
    {
      "id": "69103a210000000000991e50",
      "text": "\t[【転落人生】有名ブロガーが生活保護&借金2000万円…フリーランスの落とし穴｜アベプラ - YouTube https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2yuYpC5zUTk]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1762671138,
      "updated": 1762672028
    },
    {
      "id": "69103d9a0000000000991e80",
      "text": "\t\tマジか",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1762672028,
      "updated": 1762672031
    },
    {
      "id": "69103d9d0000000000991e82",
      "text": "\t\tブロガー時代、憧れのひとりだったが、転落しちゃうものだなぁ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1762672031,
      "updated": 1762672169
    },
    {
      "id": "69103db60000000000991e83",
      "text": "\t\tレンタルオフィスや設営の手間をケチって賃貸として保有 x4で固定費えぐい感じみたい",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1762672056,
      "updated": 1762672082
    },
    {
      "id": "69103d990000000000991e7f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1762672028,
      "updated": 1762672028
    },
    {
      "id": "691056190000000000028c65",
      "text": "[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1762678298,
      "updated": 1762678299
    },
    {
      "id": "691065ca0000000000956ac6",
      "text": "\t井戸端の[あいりすミスティリア！]のページがなぜかピン留めされていたので外しておきました。",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1762682314,
      "updated": 1762682317
    },
    {
      "id": "691065ca0000000000956ac7",
      "text": "\t\tページを見てもピン留めの意図が不明だったもので…",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1762682314,
      "updated": 1762682314
    },
    {
      "id": "691065ca0000000000956ac8",
      "text": "\t\tもし不都合があったら再度ピン留めしておいてください",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1762682314,
      "updated": 1762682314
    },
    {
      "id": "6910561c0000000000028c67",
      "text": "\t自分用のカスタムテーマのCSSが控えめに言ってうんちだったので、書き直していた",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1762678300,
      "updated": 1762694821
    },
    {
      "id": "691058090000000000028c6c",
      "text": " \t\tCosenseの一般的なUserCSSの記述スタイルにする",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1762678793,
      "updated": 1762679091
    },
    {
      "id": "6910592d0000000000028c71",
      "text": " \t\t\tモジュール化が好まれることは知っていたが、[文芸的プログラミング]の利点を理解していなかった",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1762679086,
      "updated": 1762679335
    },
    {
      "id": "6954d567000000000094cbc2",
      "text": " \t\t\tコードが簡潔なら直接編集でもノー問題であることに気づいた",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1767167335,
      "updated": 1767167335
    },
    {
      "id": "69105a070000000000028c72",
      "text": "  \t\t\tサジェストの利くテキストエディターで編集して、コード全体をコピペするほうが楽だと思っていた",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1762679304,
      "updated": 1767167339
    },
    {
      "id": "691058300000000000028c6d",
      "text": " \t\t[app.css] の変数を再利用するように",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1762678832,
      "updated": 1762679071
    },
    {
      "id": "691058a40000000000028c6f",
      "text": " \t\t\tこれだけで動作が非常に軽くなった。今までのは一体…",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1762678949,
      "updated": 1762678977
    },
    {
      "id": "69105f0c0000000000956a82",
      "text": "\t\t旧版のCSSは封印しました。",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1762680589,
      "updated": 1762680589
    },
    {
      "id": "691066d10000000000956acb",
      "text": " \t\t自分のカスタムテーマを利用している人が居る可能性がゼロではない（まあ居ないとは思う）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1762682577,
      "updated": 1767167351
    },
    {
      "id": "691056ba0000000000028c69",
      "text": "\t\t一通り書き終えたら [/customize] あたりにでも投げようと思う",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1762678458,
      "updated": 1762694201
    },
    {
      "id": "691064240000000000956a93",
      "text": " \tついでに再利用性のある箇所を切り出した",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1762681892,
      "updated": 1762681930
    },
    {
      "id": "691064240000000000956a94",
      "text": " \t\t[/customize/テーブルのセルが一定の幅を超えると改行されるようにする]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1762681892,
      "updated": 1762681893
    },
    {
      "id": "691064240000000000956a95",
      "text": " \t\t[/customize/ページを横スクロール可能にする]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1762681892,
      "updated": 1762681893
    },
    {
      "id": "691064240000000000956a96",
      "text": " \t\t[/customize/編集時にカーソル行のコントラストを上げ、他の行のコントラストを下げる]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1762681892,
      "updated": 1762681893
    },
    {
      "id": "691064240000000000956a97",
      "text": " \t\t[/customize/画面幅に応じてページの表示スケールを変更する]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1762681892,
      "updated": 1762681893
    },
    {
      "id": "6910946c0000000000ec9d4d",
      "text": " \t\t既に誰かが同じことをやってるだろうと思った解決策が検索しても見つからず、自分しかやっていなかった…ということに遭遇しがち",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1762694253,
      "updated": 1767167376
    },
    {
      "id": "691094bb0000000000ec9d4e",
      "text": " \t\t\t単純に「良い解決策ではなかったから」誰もやっていないということはそんなにない",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1762694332,
      "updated": 1762694412
    },
    {
      "id": "691095110000000000ec9d4f",
      "text": " \t\t\t即座に問題解決の最適解にたどり着く才能だけはあるのかもしれない",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1762694417,
      "updated": 1762694513
    },
    {
      "id": "691097620000000000ec9d51",
      "text": "\t「建設的に人と関われないのであれば全部自分でやりなはれ。それさえもできないのであれば一生黙ってなさい」という気持ちがある",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1762695011,
      "updated": 1767167396
    },
    {
      "id": "69105cd40000000000028c74",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1762680020,
      "updated": 1762680020
    },
    {
      "id": "6910767800000000001d6a86",
      "text": "[Hiro Aki.icon]",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1762686585,
      "updated": 1762686586
    },
    {
      "id": "6910767900000000001d6a87",
      "text": "\t今日のスロダン",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1762686586,
      "updated": 1762686593
    },
    {
      "id": "6910768000000000001d6a88",
      "text": "\t\t大体の実績取れたし、最大の問題である無強化で難易度７クリアを目指すかと試す",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1762686593,
      "updated": 1762686613
    },
    {
      "id": "6910769400000000001d6a89",
      "text": "\t\tテキトーに動かしたら１Fで倒されて、強化に胡座かいてテキトープレイしていたと思い知らされ反省",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1762686613,
      "updated": 1762686640
    },
    {
      "id": "691076af00000000001d6a8a",
      "text": "\t\t海底神殿ならなんとかなるやろ、と油断、よくない",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1762686640,
      "updated": 1762686669
    },
    {
      "id": "691087d30000000000e3d4de",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1762691028,
      "updated": 1762691029
    },
    {
      "id": "691087d50000000000e3d4df",
      "text": "[cak.icon]",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1762691030,
      "updated": 1762691033
    },
    {
      "id": "691087d90000000000e3d4e0",
      "text": " すごく ねむ〜い",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1762691033,
      "updated": 1762691616
    },
    {
      "id": "691056190000000000028c66",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1762678298,
      "updated": 1762678298
    },
    {
      "id": "6910908b00000000000054a4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762693260,
      "updated": 1762693260
    },
    {
      "id": "6910908b00000000000054a5",
      "text": "[カイト.icon]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762693260,
      "updated": 1762693262
    },
    {
      "id": "6910908d00000000000054a6",
      "text": "\t[ポケモンZA]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762693263,
      "updated": 1762693273
    },
    {
      "id": "6910909800000000000054a7",
      "text": "\t\t知ってはいたが、[ダンバル]が全く捕まらない",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762693273,
      "updated": 1762693306
    },
    {
      "id": "6910b5bc00000000000054b2",
      "text": "\t\t[ジガルデ]ですごくカッコいい",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762702781,
      "updated": 1762702800
    },
    {
      "id": "6910b95c00000000000054b3",
      "text": "\t\tストーリークリア",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762703709,
      "updated": 1762703721
    },
    {
      "id": "6910b96900000000000054b4",
      "text": "\t\t\t寄り道しまくって27時間かかった",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762703722,
      "updated": 1762703742
    },
    {
      "id": "6910944a00000000000054aa",
      "text": "\t[ポケモンSV]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762694219,
      "updated": 1762694288
    },
    {
      "id": "6910948900000000000054ab",
      "text": "\t\t[最強レイドSV]について完全に忘れてた",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762694282,
      "updated": 1762694318
    },
    {
      "id": "691094ac00000000000054ac",
      "text": "\t\t\tレイド対策用に[ハピナス]を育成しなければ",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762694318,
      "updated": 1762694354
    },
    {
      "id": "69109c0700000000000054af",
      "text": "\t\t\t[サザンドラ]、初見攻略完了",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762696200,
      "updated": 1762696223
    },
    {
      "id": "69109c8100000000000054b0",
      "text": "\t\t\t[https://gyazo.com/f3ed519b6a89859b41dae18a0b152cea]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762696322,
      "updated": 1762696344
    },
    {
      "id": "69109d4b00000000000054b1",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t[テラスタイプ「ステラ」]が強い",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762696524,
      "updated": 1762696558
    },
    {
      "id": "691090b900000000000054a8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762693306,
      "updated": 1762693306
    },
    {
      "id": "691091040000000000084c03",
      "text": "[着地鳩.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1762693381,
      "updated": 1762693382
    },
    {
      "id": "691091060000000000084c04",
      "text": " なんかしらんけど[超光戦士シャンゼリオン]が無料公開されとる！！！",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1762693383,
      "updated": 1762693404
    },
    {
      "id": "6910911e0000000000084c05",
      "text": "  Blu-rayBOXが出るからです",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1762693407,
      "updated": 1762693415
    },
    {
      "id": "691093ba0000000000084c06",
      "text": "  1話だけっぽい。サバじゃねぇ！をいきなり公開されても困るし妥当だな！",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1762694080,
      "updated": 1762694106
    },
    {
      "id": "691090b900000000000054a9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762693306,
      "updated": 1762693306
    },
    {
      "id": "6910a1cf00000000000aab4e",
      "text": "[mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1762697633,
      "updated": 1762697633
    },
    {
      "id": "6910a1cf00000000000aab4f",
      "text": " 昨日から猫と和解できてイチャイチャしてる",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1762697633,
      "updated": 1762697643
    },
    {
      "id": "6910c51200000000005bee72",
      "text": "  いいはなし[cak.icon][Hiro Aki.icon]",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1762706706,
      "updated": 1762733009
    },
    {
      "id": "6910a1d900000000000aab50",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/193c53ce9013eaa20457e0f866dee0f5]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1762697643,
      "updated": 1762697645
    },
    {
      "id": "6910a1fa00000000000aab52",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/2c9bf8aa6876ab80e025ad328a181d75]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1762697676,
      "updated": 1762697678
    },
    {
      "id": "6910a1ff00000000000aab54",
      "text": "  100ゴールドで復活できるのでまじで死なない",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1762697681,
      "updated": 1762698342
    },
    {
      "id": "6910a1fc00000000000aab53",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1762697678,
      "updated": 1762697678
    },
